ting delegated behavior.\n- Handling Native Image unsupported dynamic class definition errors using `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per your instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f754d2d88c3078b0169f5a649c0f08197b7aea692d10f38c2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 436, "output": 905, "cacheRead": 28160, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29501, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777706555780, "responseId": "resp_0f754d2d88c3078b0169f5a63c3bf88197848cb5d75a589f40"}}
